divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking my dog out for the evening when I saw the bright light southeast of where I live. At first it was a bright star but when it moved from left to right, I knew it was not a star. I thought my eyes were playing tricks on me, cause there is a tree branch from where I was viewing. I went to the front of my house and from there I knew this was not a star but a flying object. I only looked for a few minutes than gone to bed.
Summary: Bright star like but different colors appeared like sparkles
